Available options for zarith:

- GODI_ZARITH_ASM: enable platform-specific asm code
  Possible values: yes,no, <blank> = yes.

- GODI_ZARITH_PERF: enable performance statistics
  Possible values: yes,no, <blank> = no.

- GODI_ZARITH_RUN_TESTS: run simple tests after build
  Possible values: yes,no, <blank> = no.
